Class CSVReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.comp3111.CSVReader

  • public class CSVReader
extends java.lang.Object
    CSVReader - CSVReader is a class that can read .csv file. After reading the CSV file All the information stored into two different ArrayList data and fields. Fields store all the data title and data store the data itself all with type String.
